OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThis evening
OL,6,Fwill be dry with some late sunshine.
OL,7,FThen dry for a time before thickening
OL,8,Fcloud brings rain across all parts
OL,9,Flater in the night.
OL,10,
OL,11,CThursday:FRain will mostly clear away
OL,12,Fthrough the morning, although some
OL,13,Flight rain will linger into the
OL,14,Fafternoon, mainly over the southwest.
OL,15,FFurther rain spreads northeast in the
OL,16,Fevening. Warm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
